\id EPH
\toc2 Ephesians
\toc1 LETA NANGAN PAULTHAK PAM KAALAATHIMAK RAAK EPESUSAK
\mt2 LETA NANGAN PAULTHAK
\mt1 PAM KAALAATHIMAK RAAK EPESUSAK
\iot EPHESIANS Kuuk Thaayorrenak
\ip Leta naŋanma Paulntam pelnuŋun pam kaalaathimak raak Ephesusak. Paulnthurr leta ih'h yarri'i yumpirr peln pam kaalaathim aŋarr ŋaampurr naathih Kotunthurr warrmin koop ith nal yumpirr thurm-thurma wenenanan pilono raak thonoŋkun, warrmin moŋ raakumunak, warrmin moŋ raakun, ŋul Jesus Christ Mih Puth pork nul thananan pelnuŋun. (1.10) Nul nul yik mincmin pelnuŋun pam naŋan Kotak “Nun Kot ŋeey-narr nurr kar thono aŋarr pamthaaw thanah naŋanma Jesus Christmam.”
\ip Paul kanpa yikir, Pam Porka pelnan kanpa pam naŋan kunmicarr, Nul raak warr pelnan wothothur naŋanma Jesus Christ pam Nerŋk naŋanman ŋul nul man ke'err pelnuŋun Neeŋk-rithurr-min ulp wun-han pelnuŋun. Nul nul thil yikir, Nurr kar thono yarr naŋanma Jesus Christantam ŋul pam yirra aŋarr walmeerem nurr kempkempthe kaar yaan thorkorkurr raak i'irra.
\ip Nul kuthip pinalam rirrkan yiik ŋamp aŋarr ŋaampurr naathih pam naŋan Kot-thak kar thurmthurma yancim kathatharr naŋun Christ pam Mih Puththak: Thonoko, Pam kaalaathim peln kar pam-minc wuun nul paant-kak ith nul pam thulum Christ; iiwurr kuthirrka, peln kar pormpur pork ŋul foundation-kak raakun ith nul Christ; ŋul pinalama, peln pam kaalaathim kar paanth paathum wuun ŋul Christ nul pam naŋan.
\ip Christ nul Pam Pork ŋul curc nul kar paanth naŋan; ŋul pam kaalaathim peln kar minc-thaaw naŋan ith paant wuun pelnuŋun.
\ip Warrmin moŋ yumpirr Paulnthurr ith nul wun pam kuuk-kak naŋan Pam Porka. Nul maŋmaŋal wuun ith nul walmeerem Pam Pork ŋeeŋkmam minc pelnuŋun naŋanma Christmam. Paul kaaluŋeeyir warrmin moŋ raak korrkanpa pitim peln ŋul nul Christ ŋeeŋkmam pelnuŋun, wonpur pelnuŋun, raak warr pelnan yuuw wothotherr pelnantam. Itharrko nul Pam Pork minc ŋamplin ŋul nul raak warr kaar thonomarr ŋeeŋeem, kaal-purŋmat, yarra wothotherr kam naŋanman.
\c 1
\s1 LETA NANGAN PAUL-THAK PELNUNGUN PAM KAALAATHIMAK RAAK EPESUSAK
\s2 Kuukmin naŋan Paul-thak
\p 
\v 1 Ŋay Paul, pam kuuk-kak, ith muth wunparr Pam Porka nuh Christ kunanpun-hatha raak korrkanpa. Leta ih'h yumpirr pam kaalaathimak raak Ephesus peln pam kampur wunum thurmthurma naŋun Christ Jesusak.
\v 2 Pam Pork pam Ŋanipi pul Pam Pork Jesus Christanthurr nurrnun min ak yomparrnanah nurr kampan aŋarr yancih.
\s1 Pam Naŋanipi ŋamplin kun-micarr
\p 
\v 3 Ŋamp kuuk min ak yik naŋun Pam Porka, pam naŋanip naŋan Minh Puth Jesus Christak. Ŋamplin min yomparrnanirr ulp ith ŋamp kar thono weneyir naŋun Christak ŋul ŋamp warrmin min moŋ piitir man ŋeeŋkan kar yokun raakumunak.
\v 4 Raak kookanpantam, raak ith ŋarr oŋkorr kaarp yumpirr, Pam Porka ŋamplin kanpa kunmicarr ŋamp naŋan minc aŋarr wuunuh thaathurma naŋun Christak ŋul ŋamp rirrkir wacwaeirr iiwurr raakwarr-kaar aŋarr wunuh ruwunanpa Naŋun, ŋul ulp ŋeeŋkmam niinah...
\v 5 ŋul Nul ŋamplin kanpa kunmicarr ŋamp parr'ir naŋan aŋarr yomparrna naŋanma Jesus Christantam. Yarr i'i kaaluŋeeyim Pam Pork man ŋeeŋk naŋanman ith Nul ŋamplin kunmicarr.
\v 6 Nul yarr i'i meerenirr pam moŋthak ith Nul ŋampulŋun ŋeeŋkmam mincmin, ŋul ŋamplin muukur rokanirr raak pert naŋanmak pam Nerŋk naŋanmantam ulp Nul ŋeeŋkmam minc Naŋun.
\s1 Ŋamplin kunk thananirr kam naŋanman Pam Nerŋka
\p 
\v 7 Nul ŋamplin yerkmanirr raak warrmam kam naŋanman, raak warr wothotherr ŋul ulp Nul ŋeeŋkmam mincmin ŋampulŋun.
\v 8 Nul ŋampulŋun warrmin ih'h yomparrnanirr ŋamp kaalpiinth, pam ŋaampurr naathim, aŋarr weneha.
\v 9 Ŋul Nul rirrkan wenehanirr ŋampulŋun ith Nul rep kaaluŋeeyim paant thuurun ŋul Nul kanpa kun-micarr naŋanul yarr i'i yump-hatha maŋmaŋal aŋarr wunuh.
\v 10 Raak yuukarrath, raak min wacwacirr, Nul warrmin moŋ raak korrkanpa aŋarr puŋk therkan-hatath ikan naŋun Christak, warrmin raakumunak, warrmin raakun, ŋaa minc, naŋanma Jesusuntam.
\v 11 Naŋun Christak ŋamp warrmin thaathurma moŋ pitim kar Kotunthurr kanpa kunmicarr ŋul Nul warrmin koop yompomparrnanirr ith Nul riiran kaalu-ŋeeyim yump-hatha.
\v 12 Ŋamp ith kaalaathim raak kookanpantam naŋun Christak ŋamp yarr i'i ak wun kar Nul Pam Pork thakiraaw wacwacirr.
\s1 Ŋamplin min yomparrnanirr Ŋeenk-rithurr-minthurr
\p 
\v 13 Nurr yorrpnurrp naŋun kaalaathim raak ith nurr kuuk mincminc ŋeeyir, ulp kuthip minthurr nurrnun kunk thananirr. Ŋul ulp nurr kanpa kaalaathim, nurrnun pam kaalpiinth yomparrnanirr Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min-thurr ulp nuh man ke'err Pam Porka.
\p 
\v 14 Nurr nuh kanpa piitir ritar ŋul ulp nurrnun ŋuul reekhan mincminc Christanthurr, nurr Pam Pork wacwacirr aŋarr kunanpun-hatna raak ithrrath.
\s1 Kuukmin yikir Naŋun pam kaalpiinth aŋarr weneha
\p 
\v 15 Ŋay Paul kaaluŋeeyir nurr kaalaathim naŋun Jesus, Pam Thulumun ŋul nurr pam kaalaathimak ŋeeŋkmam.
\v 16 Ŋay nurrŋun prayrirk raak yirr, raak yirr ŋul ŋay nurrnun kaalu-ŋeeŋeem kuukmin ŋathanman naŋun Pam Porka.
\v 17 Ŋul nul Pam Pork naŋan Min Puth Jesus Christak, pam Naŋanipi ith Pam miiŋak niihin, nurrnun pam kaalpiinth aŋarr yomparrnanan nurr warrmin wacwacirr aŋarr ŋaampurr naath-hancih naŋanma, ŋul nurr Nuh walmeeremah.
\v 18 Ŋul nurr pam kaalpiinth aŋarr weneha ŋul nurr kaal-kaalu ak kalir ith Nul man ke'err ŋul ith nurrnun muunur ŋul warrmin wacwacirr naŋan aŋarr ŋaampurr naathih ith Nul nurrnun reek-han pam naŋan.
\v 19 Ŋul ŋay kuukmin yik naŋun Pam Porka Nul piinthaarrn minc ŋamplin aŋarr yomparrhancih pam kaalaathim ŋul Nul minc pam piinthaarrn wacwacirr mit naŋan aŋarr rirk-hatha:
\v 20 Ulp Nul Christak yomparrnanirr, raak ŋan? Ith Nul nuh watpam kunk thananirr ŋul Nul nuh niinanirr punth mal naŋanman iikan raakumunak.
\v 21 Nul ikan putpun pam thakiraaw minc ŋul mih puth yirryirram kopkop wuun naŋun, pelnuŋun pam thulumun, pelnuŋun mih punth-kokon. Namp naŋan min wacwacirr, namp pelnan pam yirra, pokon, yorr raakun, ŋuul raakumunak.
\v 22 Pam Pork, Kotunthurr warrmin moŋ wunparr kokopon thamur naŋanmak Jesus Christak ŋul Nul ulp thananirr nuh Pam Keeŋ pork aŋarr wunuh pam kaalaathim moŋthak.
\v 23 Peln ulp pam curcak kar yokun pam-minc naŋan Christak ith ŋamal minc korrkanpa raak moŋthak ithrrath korrkanpa.
\c 2
\s1 Kar pam watp kanaŋkarr man ŋeeŋkan
\p 
\v 1 Nurrnun Pam Porka kunk thananirr, nurr kanpath pam watp wunum raak warr-kak yancim raak ŋanc kaar ŋeeyimpa;
\v 2 ŋul nurr kar pam waal yancim kanaŋkarr raak warr wuump yumpum kar yokun pam moŋthurr, ŋul mih puth waŋwarr ŋeeyimpa nul raak pert naŋan rep yancim raak korrkanpa, nul pam kululeekir ith kuukthaaw naŋan Pam Porka kaar ŋeeyir.
\v 3 Ŋaa minc, ŋamp kuukthaaw warr thurma minc yikim yorrpnurrp pelnuŋun, ŋamp kermper-thaaw-nurr maŋmaŋal wuump wenehanam, ŋul ŋamp warrmin warr wakam ith rirpirr pam mincum, paant thuurmam. Ŋamp Pam Pork ŋeeŋkul rancinirr kar yokun pam moŋthurr okun raakun.
\s1 Kar pam kunk yorr man ŋeeŋkan
\p 
\v 4 Ŋaa minc, Pam Pork nul ŋeeŋkmam minc pama ŋul Nul raak warr ŋamplin warr wothothuh.
\v 5-6 Ŋawoy, ŋul ŋamp kar pam watp wunum raak warraŋan ŋul Nul ŋamplin kunk thananirr thurma Ŋan Waahancin ith Nul ŋeeŋkmam pama ŋul Nul ŋamplin kunk thananirr. Nul ŋamplin thurmthurma kunk rirkanirr ŋul Nul ŋamplin niinanirr raak puŋk naŋanmak raakumunak naŋanma Christ Jesusantam. (Iiwurr ith ŋamp raak warr ŋampulntam woonp ulp ŋamplin kaal-pinirmnanirr ŋeeŋk nerp naŋanman-thurr Nul ŋamplin kunk thananirr naŋun Christak, ŋul Nul ŋamplin aŋarr irrkan rirkan thaathurma wene-han ŋul ŋamp aŋarr thaathurma niihin ikan raakumunak raak ith ikan nul Jesus Christ niin-hat.)
\v 7 Ŋul nul raak ŋuul yup Nul aŋarrp meerenah pam kaalaathimak Nul ŋampulŋun ŋeeŋkmam wacwacirr ith Nul muukur thoŋkur ŋampulŋun naŋanma Christ Jesusantam.
\v 8 Ŋawoy, Nul nurrŋun ŋeeŋkmam, nurrnun kunk thananirr ith nurr kaalaathirr; pamal riiran kaarp yumpirr. Ulp yuur wuthan naŋanma Kotantam,
\v 9 mit min nurruntam kaarp, pam yirraman kaar aŋarr kumun maakurrna.
\v 10 Ŋamplin Nul yumpirr yuur naŋanman ŋamp mit min aŋarr rirkuh naŋanma Jesus Christmam, ulp Kotunthurr kanpa minirpunirr ŋamp yarri'i aŋarr wacirr yancih.
\s1 Ŋamplin pal thoŋkanirr kam naŋanmak
\p 
\v 11 Wey, nurr kirri kaaluŋeey, nurr kanpa kar pam Jew kaarpi ulp petan yuuru yakum kermper-thaaw-thak, nurr pam yirrth yancim ŋul ith waanir ‘ŋeeŋk rirp kaarp yaakir’ peln pam ŋeeŋk rirp yuuru yakim yikir.
\v 12 Ŋul raak awith nurr Christ-kaar yancim, nurr pam korrpal wunum thorkurr niinim raak puŋk pam Israelantam, ŋul nurr kar pam yirrth wunum pam ŋooŋkom warrmin ith man ke'err Pam Porka ŋul nurr Kot-kaar yancim rirmurr raakun, nurr Nuh kaaluŋeeyim kaarp kanaŋkarr.
\v 13 Raak ith nurr kanpath pam thorkurr wunum Christ Jesusantam ŋul nurr yorr ih'h thaapirri thoŋkur kam naŋanman Christak.
\s1 Christ Nul pam kampur ŋamplin
\p 
\v 14 Nulnulur pam kampur ŋallin, Ŋallin kuthirr Nul thono wenehanirr ŋul Nul raak muth kana rumparrnanirr ulp werŋka thanam ŋalŋun.
\v 15 Nul Jesusun pam-minc naŋanman ŋamplin pamthaaw wenehanirr, ŋamplin Raakwarra kaar aŋarr koothakarr ko'ohancih raak warr ŋampulntaman, ŋul ŋallin kuthirr pam Jewnthurr pam yirraman kar thono yomparrnanirr naŋanman Christanthurr, ŋul ŋal kampan wuun thurmthurma.
\v 16 Nul yarr i'i pulnun kuthirr kar thono wenehanirr yuk crossantam ruwunanpa Pam Porka pam-minc thono naŋanman, ŋul Nul pulnun maŋmaŋal yomparrnanirr pam kuthirr ulp wakurrnam.
\v 17 Nul ulp Jesus iiwal yat ŋul kuuk yikir nurrnuŋun nurr pam thorkurr minc niinim, nurr kampan aŋarr weneha ŋul yorrpnurrp pelnuŋun pam thaapthaapirri niinim.
\v 18 Nul Ŋan Waaharr ŋamplin ŋumanirr, thaap-thaapirri wenehanirr Pam Naŋanipin ŋamplin pam Jewn pam Gentiln kar thono aŋarr niinah pilono Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min thonthurr.
\s1 Christ nul Pam thakiraaw minc
\p 
\v 19 Ŋul yorr ih'h nurr kar pam yirr kaarpi iiwurr pam korrpal, nurr pamthaaw minc thaathurma pelnuŋun pam kaalaathimak, raak pert naŋanman Pam Porka.
\v 20 Yorr ih'h, nurrnun niinanim raak foundationak ith peln apostle-thurr yumpirr pul prophetanthurr ŋul Jesus Christ nul koothononurr minc kar therrep thaarrn wuun raakun ith;
\v 21 ŋul putpun Naŋun pormpur thanan ulp thono wenenanirr, thorkorr minc ŋul ŋamal weneyir pormpur curc min minc aŋarr yomparrna naŋanma Pam Porkam.
\v 22 Nurrnun thaathurma rokanirr Naŋun kar pormpur minc weneyir Pam Pork nul aŋarr wunuh ikan naŋanman Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-minthurr.
\c 3
\s1 Wanthantharr kunanpunirr Pam Porka curc naŋan
\p 
\v 1 Ŋul yarr i'i, naŋanma Jesus Christmam, ŋay Paul wuun prisonak nurruntam pam Gentilantam.
\v 2 Anth okun nurr kana ŋeeyir Pam Pork nul ŋeeŋkmam minc ŋathun mit ŋathanmantam nurrnuŋun.
\v 3 Nul meer rirrkan rirpinirr ŋathun warrmin ith ŋay pam ŋooŋkom niinim kar ulp ŋay kanpa ratan yumpirr ritar nurrnuŋun.
\v 4 Ŋul ith nurr leta ŋathan naath-hat ulp, nurr aŋarr kaaluŋeeyih ŋay kuthip naŋan Christak walmeerem mincmin.
\v 5 Pam kanaŋkarr pam ŋooŋkom minc, pelnan kaarp kunanpunum raakun. Ulp Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-minthurr yorrnurr meer rirrkan rirpinirr pam prophetak pam apostulak ith nul ŋanc wenehanirr yarr i'i:
\v 6 peln pam Gentile thurmthurma wun-hatath pilun pam Jewthak pam-minc thonthak naŋun Christak ŋul ŋamp pam moŋthurr pit-hatath ith Nul man ke'err kuthip min naŋanmak.
\v 7 Ŋul ŋah kunmicarr mit naŋan rirk-hatha ŋul Nul Pam Pork piinthaarrn minc-thurr ŋah kaalpiinth wenehanirr mit naŋanmak. Pam Pork-thurr ŋah mincthaaw naŋanmantam Nul piinthaarrn wenehanirr.
\s1 Pam Pork nul ŋan kaaluŋeeyim
\p 
\v 8 Ŋawoy, ŋenem, ŋay pam ŋooŋkom niinam ith pam mantam minc pelnuŋun pam kaalaathim moŋthak ŋul Nul ŋah kunmicarr ŋay kuukmin wacwacirr naŋan aŋarr kunanpunuh pam korrpalak, yarri'i, Christ Nul pam thakiraaw wacwacirr pamal nuh kaarp koop kaaluŋeeyih.
\v 9 Ŋay ak meer rirrkan yikir pam moŋthak Pam Pork Nul ŋeeŋkmam minc pam Gentilak pelnan kunk thanan-hatha. Peln ih'h kanaŋkarr pam ŋooŋkom minc niinim, yorr kana; Pam Pork riiran walmeerem ith Nul warrmin koop yumpirr thurmthurma naŋanman Jesus Christunthurr.
\v 10 Ŋul ŋene? Pam Pork nul kaalpiinth wacwacirr ŋul yorrnurr ih'h ŋamp pam kaalaathiman yarr i'i aŋarr meerenah pelnuŋun pam thulumak, mih punth-kokon, pam porkthak raakumunak.
\v 11 Ŋul nul Kotunthurr kookanpantam kun-micarr nuh Jesus Christ Pam Pork ŋamplin yomparrnan-natha raak ŋuul.
\v 12 Ŋul naŋanma Christmam ŋamp naŋun aŋarr rokuh ŋul Nul ŋamplin muukur minimnanir, maŋmaŋal, iiwurr weneth-kaar ŋul ŋamp yorr pam kaalaath wuun naŋanma.
\v 13 Ŋay yarri'i yik — meerkunwarr oŋkorr wun ŋathanma ith ŋay kaalmeer kenceyir nurruntam. Nurrnun min wacwacirr yup yomparrnanurrtha.
\s1 Kuukmin pam kaalaathim aŋarr mincmin yancih yorr
\p 
\v 14 Ŋul yarri'i ŋay ulp puŋkumun niinir ruwunanpa Pam Naŋanip naŋanman Mih Puth Jesus Christak.
\v 15 Ŋul pam moŋthurr raakumunak raakun namp kumun naŋan Pam Porka ŋamp wanurrur.
\v 16 Ŋul ulp Pam Pork ith raak warrmin moŋ-kokonak kar paath therper rancirr, Nul nurrnun piinthaarrn aŋarr wenehanan Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min naŋanman man ŋeeŋk paman.
\v 17 Ŋul ulp Christ nul ak wunur man ŋeeŋk nurrnuntaman nurrŋun pam kaalaathamak ŋul nurr pam ŋeeŋkmam aŋarr niinah kar yuk yukumun thaarrnkak irrkop piinthirr raakun.
\v 18 Nurr yarri'i kar yokun peln pam kaalaathim korrkanpa nurr aŋarr kaaluŋeeyhan Nul Kot wuun thampurr minc, wuun thorkorr minc, wuun iikop minc, wuun yuukan minc raak moŋthak.
\v 19 Ŋul ulp nurr aŋarr kaaluŋeeyih mincminc Christ nul ŋeeŋkmam wacwacirr minc pama ŋul nurr aŋarr wun thurmthurma naŋun Kotak man ŋeeŋkan, thaathaarrn mincip.
\v 20 Nul ŋamplin min yompomparr-nanancih, ŋamp wuump pokon raŋkaŋkuh iiwurr kaaluŋeeyih thil naŋanma. Nul mit pork wuump aŋarr rirkuh ŋampulŋun ŋul nul piinthaarrn wacwacirr.
\v 21 Namp naŋan ak porkpunur pam kaalaathimak naŋanma Christ Jesusuntam, thonomarr raak meer-ŋuul ŋoontma. Ŋawoy kana.
\c 4
\s1 Kuuk-thaaw peln kar thono aŋarr yancih
\p 
\v 1 Ŋay pam naŋan Pam Porka ith gaol-thak rokanirr, ŋul ŋay mincmin yik nurrnuŋun, nurr min wacwacirr aŋarr yancih kar yokun Nul ith nurrnun kanpa munarr.
\v 2 Ŋul nurr pam ŋeeŋkmam aŋarr yancih, nurr pam muukur rookur aŋarr wunuh; ŋul nurr pam yirr moŋ aŋarr yuur reekuh.
\v 3 Kar thono kirri yarr nurr, pam kampur wun Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min-thurr, pam yirryirra ŋoŋkorr yarr!
\s1 Wanthantharr ŋul kar thono than-hatha
\p 
\v 4 Pam-minc thononurr, ŋul Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min thononurr wuun, kar yokun nurrnun pam moŋ munarr nul Pam Porka nurr pilthono aŋarr thanah.
\v 5 Mih Puth thononurr, pam kaalaathim kulpuŋk thononurr thanan, baptism thononurr aŋarr kaaluŋeeyih.
\v 6 Pam Pork thononurr niihin ulp pam Naŋanip ŋamplin pam moŋthak ith wuun putpun minc raakumunak, raak korrkanpa, iikan nurrŋun pam moŋthak.
\s1 Yuur wuthan peln kar thono aŋarr than-hatha
\p 
\v 7 Ŋamplin moŋ Pam Porkunthurr yomparrnanirr ŋamp pam wacwacirr aŋarr wunuh kar yokun Christanthurr reekarr ŋamplin yirryirram.
\v 8 Ŋul yarr i'i yikir:
\q1 “Nul irrkan yat putpun,
\q1 Ŋul Nul pam prisonak katpirr,
\q1 Ŋul nul yuur-wuthan reekarr pam.” (Ps 68.18)
\p 
\v 9 Kuuk ih'h “irrkan yat-ul” wanthantharr? ŋan waanir? Yarr i'i okun? Nul kanpa irrkop wuump yat kopkopuŋkurr raakun?
\v 10 Pam ith nul irrkop reenpenat, ŋul nul ulp yokunman irrkan thaaŋkarr putpun raakumunak kankan Nul raak moŋthak aŋarr wun-hancih korrkanpa Mih Puth pam moŋthak.
\v 11 Ŋul nul pam yirram micarr peln pam kuthip-kak aŋarr yancih, yirram pam poropet, yirram pam kuthip min aŋarr yik-hancih pam korrpalak. Yirram peln pam naŋan Christak kuupum, yirram pam tica yomparrnanirr.
\s1 Yuur wuthan ŋene?
\p 
\v 12 Nul yarr i'i yumpirr peln pam kaalaathim aŋarr kaalpiinth yancih mit naŋanman ŋul peln pam-minc naŋan Christak aŋarr ticim-rirkih.
\v 13 Ŋul yarri'i ŋamp kar thono aŋarr weneha ith ŋamp kaalaath ŋul ŋamp Pam Nerŋk naŋan Kot-thak walmeerem mincmin, ŋul ŋamp pam kaalpiinth yomparrna ŋamp pam wacwacirr kar Christ aŋarr than-hancih.
\v 14 Ŋul ŋamp kar parr'ir-nurr kaarp aŋarr wunuh kar yirram ith pelnan pam warran kululeekum, ulp ith pamal manaŋkar yikum ŋul peln ulp kar yuk thorkorr puun porkan ith peln pam moŋoŋomur, man thono kaarp yikum pelnan aŋarr warr wenehanancih.
\v 15 Ŋamp pam ŋeeŋkmam ak wuun, ŋamp kuuk mincminc aŋarr yik-hancih, ŋamp pam min aŋarr piinth-hancih warrmin moŋthak kar Christ nul pam Thulum ŋamplin.
\v 16 Ith naŋanma Christmam, pam-minc ŋamplin, yaŋkar, yuur, muth, paant kar thono aŋarr matanah pilono, pil, puŋk, punt, tendon ith kempkempthe mit naŋan yumpurrtha, peln koop pam-minc piinthinhancih ŋul pam ŋeeŋkmam aŋarr yancih, ŋul min aŋarr yomparrna.
\s1 Yarra wak ‘pam meerkanam’
\p 
\v 17 Yarri'i ŋay yiik, ŋay kunanpunur Pam Porkam nurrnuŋun — oŋkorr yarr kar yokun peln pam korrpal yancim ŋul peln waal wunum paant thuur pelnantaman.
\v 18 Peln kar walinthul, waal wunum, peln thorkurr yancim Pam Porkam, peln pokon kaaluŋeeyim ŋul peln thaarrn minc man ŋeeŋkan.
\v 19 Peln pokon ŋaatheyir ŋul peln ŋorŋur yancim pam-mincun, ŋul mit warr rirkim, warrmin koop wothothum, ulp rirrkir kaarp wunum.
\v 20 Wey, nurr kar ih'nul Christunthurr nurrnuŋun kaarp kunanpunum!
\v 21 Nurr nuh Christ wuump ŋeeyhat? Ŋul Nul nurrnuŋun wuump kaar yik-hat? Christ Nul kuuk mincminc yiik.
\v 22 Mit warr naŋan ‘pam meerkanaman’ kirri yarra thak paant thuurum, nurr mit warr wuwum, nurr pam warr wunum.
\s1 ‘Pam puukam’ kirri rok
\p 
\v 23 Kar pam puukam kirri yarr paant thuurun, man ŋeeŋk nurrnuntaman.
\v 24 Pam Porka nih puukam wenenanirr: kirri yarrthurr kar pam ulp, kunkunanp, rirrkir minc kar Kot!
\v 25 Pam moŋoŋomur oŋkorr wun, kuuk mincminc-nurr yiik pama, ŋamp pamthaaw wuun pilono.
\v 26 Anth okun nunt pacarr, pam warran naam oŋkorr yarr; pam kampur wene puŋ kaarp munthirr.
\v 27 Waŋ warra naŋkanunt oŋkorr pam thaayuur reekurr ŋul nih nul pam warram-hanir.
\v 28 Pam ith warrmin repam, oŋkorr rep, ak mit rirk yuur naŋanman, mit min rirk-narr nul pam raak-rirkir-kaar aŋarr reekah nuh.
\v 29 Kuuk-thaaw warr oŋkorr yiik, kuuk min yik pam yirr aŋarr maŋmaŋal yomparrnanah, pam moŋ aŋarr ŋeeŋkmam thananah thurmthurma.
\s1 Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min oŋkorr kululeek
\p 
\v 30 Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min naŋan Pam Porka oŋkorr kululeek! Nul ulp nurrnun pam muurk thananirr Nul raak ith yuukarra nurrnun min aŋarr yomparrnanancih.
\v 31 Oŋkorr pac, oŋkorr ŋeeŋkuluuth, meer-warran oŋkorr naam, pam kuuk moŋ-kak oŋkorr than, pam rakakir oŋkorr wun — kuukthaaw warr oŋkorr yiik, pam kampur wene.
\v 32 Pam ŋeeŋkmam yarr thurmthurma pam moŋthak, pam kampur wun man ŋeeŋk minin, pam yirram oŋkorr pac nurr aŋarr yancih kar yokun Pam Pork, ith naŋun Christak raak warr naŋkan kana wothotherr.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Yarri'i, Pam Pork nuh wak, kar parr'ir ulp Nul pelnuŋun ŋeeŋkmam.
\v 2 Nurr pam ŋeeŋkmam yarr kar yokunman Christ ith ŋampulŋun ŋeeŋkmam niinim. Ŋul nul naŋanul reekeyir Nuh Kot ŋul peln nuh therŋarr watp Nul raak warr ŋamplin aŋarr yarra wothoth-hatha ŋul maŋmaŋal Pam Pork naŋanma ŋul Nul ruwunanpa Naŋun Kot-thak niinim kar mih kermper ith kuŋun min minc reekurrur naŋanul.
\v 3 Warrmin ith warr, kar paanth yirr waathim, warrmin ith ŋorŋur, warrmin ith kar pam warrmin koop wothothum ŋul ŋuunp waatheyir, nurr oŋkorr wanan pama ŋul yarr i'i min wacwacirr pam kaalaathimak.
\v 4 Kuukthaaw ŋorŋur oŋkorr wanan, kuuk waal oŋkorr yik, kuukthaaw woocwocurr min kaarp. Yarri'i min ith nurr kuuk thaakuump aŋarr yikih naŋun Pam Porka.
\v 5 Ih'nul kirri ŋeey-le, pam ith paanth moŋ wakakim, pam ith kar ŋorŋur yancim, pam ith warrmin moŋ wothothum kar pam god naŋan, pam ulp kaarp yan Raak puŋkun naŋan Christak naŋan Kot-thak.
\v 6 Pam yirram oŋkorr muth wunp nurrnuŋun moŋom-hatha kuuk-thaawam manaŋkar-mam: nuh thakan! Ith nurr yarr i'i yuumpurrtha, Pam Pork nul pac-han pam moŋ ulp ith kuuk-thaaw naŋan kaar ŋeeyim.
\v 7 Yarri'i oŋkorr yarr pelnuŋun thurma.
\v 8 Nurr kanaŋkarr yancim kar raak ŋurnturnthurr-ak, yorr ih'h nurr raak miiŋin yaan naŋan Pam Porka. Kirri, wacwacirr yarr kar pam miiŋ-kak.
\v 9 Pam ith yancim miiŋ-thak nul mit kunkunanp riirk, ŋul min wacwacirr wuun kar pam mincminc.
\v 10 Ŋul nurr meren-nan warrmin ith Pam Pork maŋmaŋal wenehanan Nuh.
\v 11 Oŋkorr thurmthurma yarr pelnuŋun pamal mit warr rirkum kar raak ŋurnturnthurrak, kirri pelnan wananharr!
\v 12 Ŋamp ak pancir-rirk yan warrmin warrmam ith pam yirraman wananam-nurr mit warrmam ulp peln yumpum rep.
\s1 Kar Parr'ir thit-kak aŋarr yancih
\p 
\v 13 Ith warrmin moŋ riirrkan wene raak miiŋ-thak ŋul aŋarr naathih pelnan, ŋawoy, warrmin ulp naathim pamal ŋul kar thit-kak yomparr.
\v 14 Nul yarri'i yikim, “Pinar wun, nunt pam ith wut wunum, rirk-le watpam ŋul Christunthurr Nul thiimp-han naŋkun.”
\v 15 Wacwacirr naath-harr ŋul nurr kar pam kaalpiinth aŋarr yancih, kar pam waal kaarp, pilwacirr yarr!
\v 16 Mit yirram naŋkan kirri rirkic, yuparr oŋkorr, raak yorr ih'h raak warr.
\v 17 Kar pam waal oŋkorr wun, ith Pam Porka kunmicarr kirri kaaluŋeey!
\s1 Kirri yarr Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-min-kak
\p 
\v 18 Ŋok paapaath oŋkorr muŋk nunt drunk-rirk aŋarr yancih. Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-minthurr okun ak wuun mincmin iikan naŋkun.
\v 19 Kar pamthaaw minc kirri yarr ith nurr kuukthaaw wacwacirr yiikurrur thaathurma paman, wuuc naŋan Pam Porka mi'iharr ŋul nurr maŋmaŋal aŋarr yancih ŋeeŋk nerp nurrnuntaman.
\v 20 Kuuk thaakuump thaathaawan yik naŋun Pam Porka, pam Naŋanipin, iikan namp naŋanman Jesus Christak.
\s1 Paanth Pam
\p 
\v 21 Thaathurma wenehanurr nip, kuuk kaalu nip ŋeeŋeeyurr waat patheyir naŋanma ruwunanpa Kot-thak.
\s1 Ŋeey pam nurrnun nurr Paanthurra
\p 
\v 22 Nurr paanthurra, ŋeey pam naŋkan, kar ith nunt Pam Pork ŋeeŋeem.
\v 23 Pam meermele nul mih puth naŋun paanthu kar ih'nul yorrpnurrp yarr i'i Nul Christ nul mih Puth curcak. Ŋul nul Christ-anthurr riiran curc kunk thananir ulp mincthaaw naŋan.
\v 24 Ŋul yarri'i kar paanth paathumun pam meermele pelnan kuuk kaaluŋeeyim mincmin ŋul yorrpnurrp curcunthurr kaaluŋeem nuh Christ.
\s1 Ŋeeŋkmam niin paanth paathumun nurr pam meermele
\p 
\v 25 Nurr pam meermele, ŋeeŋkmam niin paanth nurruntamak kar yorrpnurrp ith Christ nul ŋeeŋkmam niinim Curcak, ŋul naŋanul therŋeyir, kaalmeer kenceyir, wonpur Nul naŋun,
\v 26 Nul aŋarr curc ŋanc wunp-hancih ŋul rirrkirm-hanancih kuukul naŋanman, kar ŋokel kuuk naŋanman curc rirrkirm-hanirr,
\v 27 nul aŋarr curc reekurrur naŋanul, min wenehanurrur rirrkir, raak warrkaar, thatir, pilpuuŋk pokon, mincthaaw muny pokon, warr pokon, ŋul yarri'i curc nul rirrkir ak than-nan, raak warr-kaar, ŋanc thaarrn wacwacirr.
\v 28 Pam nul paanthu ŋeeŋkmam ak niin kar ith nul mincthaaw naŋanul kar mincthaaw nuluth wacwacirr piiturr. Ith nul pam ŋeeŋkmam niin naŋun paanthu, nul naŋanul yorrpnurrp piiturr.
\v 29 Pam yirryirram ŋamp mincthaaw ŋamplin kaarp meer warran naathurrur. Ŋawoy, ulp ŋamp mayil piipiinthinurr ulp wacwacirr piinthinir kar ith Christunthurr yomparrnanir Curcthak.
\v 30 Ŋamp pam kulpuŋk mincthaaw naŋan, kermper, piinth naŋan.
\v 31 Yarr i'i Paypul yikir:
\q1 “Peln pamal yarr i'i pam naŋanip thak-han, pam naŋanam
\q1 yorrpnurrp, ŋul pul thaathurma wene paanth paathum
\q1 naŋanman pamal paanth naŋanman, ŋul pul paanth
\q1 naŋanman kar thono yomparr.” (Gen 2:23-24)
\p 
\v 32 Kuuk ulp warr ŋamal minc Kotunthurr rirpinirr Paypulntam ŋul ŋay kaalaathir kuuk ith kar yokunman Christanthurr pul Curcunthurr.
\v 33 Ulp nurrŋun yorrpnurrp min pam meermele moŋthak. Nurr paanth paathum-ak ŋeeŋkmam niin, kar nul riiran, ŋul paanth-paathum yorrpnurrp peln kuuk thakirmin ak yik pelnuŋun pam melencin.
\c 6
\s1 “Pam paanth parr'ir-kokonak”
\p 
\v 1 Wey, parr'ir ŋe! Ih'nth nurrnun kunanp wene-hanir wacwacirr kaalaath-hatha pam naŋanaman pam naŋanipin. Ih'nul wacwacirr yomparr-nanir Pam Porka.
\v 2 Kuuk wacwacirr yik pam naŋanaman pam naŋanipin. Ih'nul kuuk kookanpa naŋanma Kotantam nul kanpa man ke'err ŋamplin min wenehanir naŋanma kuuk thaawam.
\v 3 Ŋul yarr i'i: “min aŋarr niinah raak meerŋuul ŋoontma raak kaal thorkorrtha raakun.”
\v 4 Pam naŋanip, waat wacwacirr oŋkorr, parr'ir yorrp oŋkorr ŋeeŋkul-oŋkan pelnan. Yarr i'i, piinthin pelnan raak Christianak, koothakarr ko'o pelnan, ith peln waat wacirr yaan peln, wacwacirr yikan pelnan kuuk Pam Porka wak-hatha.
\s1 Mih puth ŋeeyharr, nurr pam mit rirkum
\p 
\v 5 Pam mit rirkim, pam mih puth nurrnun kirri ŋeey-harr raakun, kar weneth minŋim ŋul ŋerŋarr-akum man ŋeeŋk minthak kar y-okunman naŋun Christak.
\v 6 Moŋoŋomur oŋkorr kar pam yirramthurr ith man thono kaar yiik ruwunanpa mih puth-thak ulp. Nurr mincminc wun kar pam mit rirkum naŋan Christak. Pam Pork ŋeey-le man ŋeeŋk nurrnuntaman.
\v 7 Mit min maŋmaŋal rirk ruwunanpa Pam Porkan, ruwunanpa paman kaarp.
\v 8 Kaaluŋeey-le, mit min ŋanŋanerr ith nul pamal yumpirr pam ulp Pam Porka warrmin yokunmannurrp reek-han nuh, ith nul mih puth-kak wunum iiwurr nul mih puth-pokonp.
\v 9 Nurr pam mih puth, pam mit rirkim nurrnan oŋkorr pac! Pam kampur wun pelnuŋun kar yokunman Pam Mih Puth nurrnun iiwurr pelnan, ikan niihin raakumunak, ŋul Nul pam pork iiwurr pam mit-rirkum kaar kunmicim. Nul pulnuŋun ŋeeŋkmam kuthirrman yokunman-nurrp.
\s1 Armour naŋan Pam Porka kirri rok
\p 
\v 10 Ŋawoy, pamthaaw ŋathan, piinthaarrn than-harr ikan naŋun Pam Porka ith nurrnun piinthaarrn yomparr-nanurrtha.
\v 11 Warrmin pam warr thertherŋ-hatha moŋ naŋan Pam Porka kirri rok nunt pam piinthaarrn aŋarr pilwacirr than-hancih ruwunanpa Waŋ warran ith manaŋkar yorrpnurrp ŋampulŋun.
\v 12 Ŋamp pam warr kermper-kak kamkak kaarp therŋum, ŋamp waŋ-warr moŋ therŋurrtha ith mih puth-kak, ith pam pork-kak ith pam thulumkak raak ŋurnturnthurrak ŋul ŋamp pilwacirr thanan pelnan waŋwarr moŋ minc therŋ-hatha raakumun pelnantaman raak ithrrath.
\v 13 Yarri'i mimp armour moŋ naŋan Pam Porka rok-le nunt pam piinthaarrn aŋarr than-han raak warran awith ŋul thonomarr aŋarr than-hancih kaal-piinth!
\v 14 Ŋawoy, than-le mincminc man petan-kak ŋul moŋomur kaarp. Kunkunanp minc wun kar yuk putun-kak kar breastplate wacwacirr rok-le man ruwan.
\v 15 Kirri yarr yuk shoe pam kampur-kak pam yirram maŋmaŋal aŋarr wene-hanancih kuthip minmam.
\v 16 Ŋaa minc, yuk putun kirri kal, kaalaath naŋanma nunt kirk mant paathkak moŋ naŋan waŋ warra aŋarr thakanah.
\v 17 Nih kunk-thananirr ŋul ulp kar helmet paant naŋkanmak. Ith kuuk-thaaw naŋan Pam Porka kar nayp pork naŋan Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-minthak; kirri katp-le pulnun!
\s1 Kar pam piinthaarrn than!
\p 
\v 18 Raŋkaŋk naŋun Pam Porka man ŋeeŋk naŋkanman warrmin min Nul nih aŋarr reek-hatha Ŋeeŋk-rithurr-minthurr. Pil wacirr ŋul yik minc-min naŋun Kot-thak Nul pam kaalathim moŋ min wenehanhatha,
\v 19 Kuukmin yik Naŋun ŋathanma Nul ŋah kuukthaaw wacwacirr aŋarr wan-hanah ŋay kuuk-thaaw putpun aŋarr yikah. Ŋul pam korrpaln ŋeeyhan kuthip min naŋan Christak.
\v 20 Ŋay pam kuthip-kak ŋah katharr pormpur gaolthak. Nurr wey, raŋkaŋk-le, ŋay kuthipmin kaalpiinth aŋarr yikah ŋul ŋay minc warr yik-hancih.
\s1 Leta naŋan kerpe-hanirr
\p 
\v 21 Pamthaaw minc ŋathan Tychicus ith pam mit rirkum min naŋan Pam Porka nul warrmin moŋ wanhan nurrnuŋun ŋul nurr ŋathanma warrmin ŋathan moŋ aŋarr ŋeey-han ith ŋay min wuun.
\v 22 Ŋay nuh muth wunp nurrnuŋun yokunman yarri'i, nurr aŋarr kaaluŋeeyih ŋancin kana, yuur moŋon ŋul nul man ŋeeŋk nurrnan aŋarr maŋmaŋal wene-hanancih ŋancinantamantam.
\v 23 Pam kampur wun, pamthaaw ŋathan, pam ŋeeŋkmam niin ith nurr kaalaathim naŋanma Pam Porkam ulp ŋeeŋkmam nurrnuŋun, ulpnurrp Pam Naŋanipi pul Mih Puth Jesus Christanthurr.
\v 24 Kot nul min wenehanan pam moŋ ulp ŋeeŋkmam minc niinim naŋun Mih Puth Jesus Christak. Ŋawoy, leta ih'nul kana kerpir. 
